      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home a fantastic vehicle that's been well-loved and is ready for many more miles! This car is in solid, good condition, offering a smooth ride and dependable performance that you can count on for your daily travels. It shows some light, honest signs of use, but it has been maintained with care and is mechanically sound. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value for anyone looking for a reliable ride today!",
