    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no imperfections, while the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in peak original condition.",
