    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously cared for. It drives like an absolute dream and is truly a rare find in this kind of shape. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the crazy dealership markup, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
