      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46), a superlative example of Bavarian engineering. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, this unit features six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is flawless, featuring documented preventative subframe reinforcement and a completely refreshed suspension utilizing OEM bushings and dampers. This vehicle boasts original paint with a mirror finish and an interior that shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically perfect, collector-tier specimen for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
