    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies the typical used car market. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster with a mirror-like finish, free from any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats are supple without any bolster wear, and the dashboard remains pristine. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule at authorized dealerships with full documentation included. The engine bay is spotless, reflecting the care this car has received. With low original miles and a single-owner history, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Serious inquiries only for this turn-key masterpiece.",
